Third-party domain-list integration
===================================

The optional community-list feature can download selected service lists at
runtime from:

    https://github.com/itdoginfo/allow-domains

The domain-list contents from that repository are not included in this source
tree or in the OpenWrt package. As of June 19, 2026, the upstream repository
does not contain a license file. Public availability on GitHub does not by
itself grant redistribution rights.

Downloaded content is controlled by its upstream authors and is not covered by
this project's MIT License. Users who enable the integration are responsible
for determining whether their use of the external lists is permitted.

The project-maintained lists under `luci-ikev2-domains/local-services/` are
part of this repository and are covered by the MIT License.

ISRG root certificates
======================

The package includes the public ISRG Root X1 and ISRG Root X2 trust anchors
published by Let's Encrypt:

    https://letsencrypt.org/certificates/

They are included as certificate data used to verify ACME downloads and are
not authored by this project.
